Human regular	30–60 min	2 h	6–8 h
Technosphere inhaled insulin	5–15 min	1 h	3 h
Human NPH	2–4 h	6–7 h	10–20 h
Insulin glargine	0.5–1 h	Flat	~24 h
Insulin detemir	0.5–1 h	Flat	17 h
