 • Colesevelam hydrochloride	Bile acid binder: Lowers glucose through unknown mechanisms	Reduces glucose levels	Type 2 diabetes	Oral • 24-h duration of action • Toxicity: Constipation, indigestion, flatulence
DOPAMINE AGONIST
 • Bromocriptine	D2 receptor agonist: Lowers glucose through unknown mechanism	Reduces glucose levels	Type 2 diabetes	Oral • 24-h action • Toxicity: Nausea, vomiting, dizziness, headache
